    description: "Hampi's most hyper-local snack — spiced puffed rice tossed with turmeric, garlic, onions, and peanuts, paired with hot masala chai. This tiny riverside spot near Purandara Dasara Mantapa is off every tourist trail. Two plates and two chais for ₹80.",
