    description: 'Real wood-oven pizza on Hippie Island — rare for Hampi. Thakur and Sharmilla started this in 1998 as a two-person operation; it is now a beloved institution with its own guesthouse. One of the few spots serving non-veg across the river. Evening bonfires under coconut trees seal the deal.',
