    description: "Karnataka's signature comfort food — hot lentil-rice cooked with mixed vegetables and a freshly ground spice powder of coriander, dried chillies, coconut, and cinnamon. Ravi's Rose in Hampi Bazaar serves it alongside masala dosa and idli-vada. Spicy, tangy, deeply aromatic — one bowl and you will understand why the whole state swears by it.",
