    title: 'Kerala Fish Curry Meals',
    location: 'Juicy Cafe',
    description: "The most authentic Kerala-style food on the cliff at rock-bottom prices. Rice, fish curry, thoran, sambar, and rasam on a steel plate — exactly how locals eat lunch. No frills, no menu confusion, just honest Kerala meals from 6 AM. ₹100-300 for two.",
