    description: "Pearl spot fish marinated in red chilli-turmeric paste, wrapped in banana leaf, and slow-grilled — Kerala's signature seafood dish. This 60-year-old toddy shop on Attingal Road also serves duck curry, meen thala curry, and crab roast alongside fresh toddy. Families welcome. ₹400-600 for two.",
