    title: 'Appam & Egg Curry',
    location: 'Tickety Boo',
    description: "A social enterprise cafe that employs people with disabilities — and happens to serve beautiful appam, egg dosa, and omelettes. Morning-only breakfast (7-11 AM) and evening snacks (4-11 PM). The appam is lacy, soft-centred, and scoops up the egg curry perfectly. ₹100-300 for two.",
