    title: 'Puttu & Kadala Curry',
    location: 'Local Tea Shops, Varkala Town',
    description: "Steamed rice-coconut logs broken open and paired with spicy black chickpea curry — Kerala's everyday breakfast. Skip the cliff tourist strip; walk into Varkala town and find any tea shop with a steel puttu maker steaming at 7 AM. A plate costs ₹30-50.",
